{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":788,"text":"My dream is to build the world's first"},{"time":2970,"text":"underground park in New York City."},{"time":5294,"text":"Now, why would someone want\nto build an underground park,"},{"time":7841,"text":"and why in New York City?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":11038,"text":"These three tough little buggers"},{"time":12562,"text":"are, on the left, my grandmother, age five,"},{"time":15778,"text":"and then her sister and brother,"},{"time":17128,"text":"ages 11 and nine."},{"time":18666,"text":"This photo was taken just before they left"},{"time":20863,"text":"from Italy to immigrate to the United States,"},{"time":23471,"text":"just about a century ago."},{"time":25982,"text":"And like many immigrants at the time,"},{"time":27377,"text":"they arrived on the Lower East Side"},{"time":29090,"text":"in New York City"},{"time":30291,"text":"and they encountered a crazy melting pot."},{"time":33160,"text":"What was amazing about their generation"},{"time":34567,"text":"was that they were not only building new lives"},{"time":37627,"text":"in this new, unfamiliar area,"},{"time":39750,"text":"but they were also literally building the city."},{"time":42346,"text":"I've always been fascinated by those decades"},{"time":44479,"text":"and by that history,"},{"time":45799,"text":"and I would often beg my grandmother"},{"time":48278,"text":"to tell me as many stories as possible"},{"time":49947,"text":"about the old New York."},{"time":51955,"text":"But she would often just shrug it off,"},{"time":54133,"text":"tell me to eat more meatballs, more pasta,"},{"time":56383,"text":"and so I very rarely got"},{"time":58260,"text":"any of the history that I wanted to hear about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61355,"text":"The New York City that I encountered"},{"time":62616,"text":"felt pretty built up."},{"time":64514,"text":"I always knew as a kid that I wanted"},{"time":66711,"text":"to make a difference, and to somehow"},{"time":68229,"text":"make the world more beautiful, more interesting"},{"time":70435,"text":"and more just."},{"time":71462,"text":"I just didn't really know how."},{"time":73259,"text":"At first, I thought I wanted to go work abroad,"},{"time":74947,"text":"so I took a job with UNICEF in Kenya."},{"time":77366,"text":"But it felt weird to me that I knew more about"},{"time":79481,"text":"local Kenyan politics than the\npolitics of my own hometown."},{"time":83115,"text":"I took a job with the City of New York,"},{"time":85121,"text":"but very quickly felt frustrated"},{"time":87270,"text":"with the slowness of government bureaucracy."},{"time":90308,"text":"I even took a job at Google,"},{"time":92013,"text":"where very fast I drank the Kool-Aid"},{"time":95110,"text":"and believed almost wholeheartedly"},{"time":96856,"text":"that technology could solve all social problems."},{"time":100474,"text":"But I still didn't feel like I was\nmaking the world a better place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103960,"text":"It was in 2009 that my friend"},{"time":105819,"text":"and now business partner James Ramsey"},{"time":107787,"text":"alerted me to the location of a pretty spectacular site,"},{"time":110881,"text":"which is this."},{"time":112331,"text":"This is the former trolley terminal"},{"time":114166,"text":"that was the depot for passengers"},{"time":116744,"text":"traveling over the Williamsburg Bridge"},{"time":118648,"text":"from Brooklyn to Manhattan,"},{"time":120932,"text":"and it was open between 1908 and 1948,"},{"time":123701,"text":"just around the time when my grandparents were"},{"time":126143,"text":"living right in the area."},{"time":127992,"text":"And we learned also that the site"},{"time":129640,"text":"was entirely abandoned in 1948."},{"time":132882,"text":"Fascinated by this discovery,"},{"time":134805,"text":"we begged the authorities to draw us into the space,"},{"time":137933,"text":"and we finally got a tour,"},{"time":139440,"text":"and this is what we saw."},{"time":141590,"text":"Now, this photo doesn't really do it justice."},{"time":143300,"text":"It's kind of hard to imagine the unbelievably magical"},{"time":145960,"text":"feeling that you have when you get in this space."},{"time":148119,"text":"It's a football field of unused land"},{"time":151807,"text":"immediately below a very crowded area of the city,"},{"time":155210,"text":"and it almost feels like you're Indiana Jones"},{"time":157345,"text":"on an archaeological dig,"},{"time":159060,"text":"and all the details are all still there."},{"time":160833,"text":"It's really pretty remarkable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162801,"text":"Now, the site itself is located at the very heart"},{"time":165401,"text":"of the Lower East Side,"},{"time":167270,"text":"and today it still remains one of the most"},{"time":168766,"text":"crowded neighborhoods in the city."},{"time":170757,"text":"New York City has two thirds the green space"},{"time":172557,"text":"per resident as other big cities,"},{"time":174605,"text":"and this neighborhood as one tenth the green space."},{"time":177778,"text":"So we immediately started thinking about how we"},{"time":179601,"text":"could take this site and turn it into something"},{"time":181671,"text":"that could be used for the public,"},{"time":183058,"text":"but also could potentially even be green."},{"time":185810,"text":"Our plan, in a nutshell,"},{"time":187140,"text":"is to draw natural sunlight underground"},{"time":189841,"text":"using a simple system that\nharvests sunlight above the street,"},{"time":192944,"text":"directs it below the city sidewalks,"},{"time":195380,"text":"and would allow plants and trees to grow"},{"time":197310,"text":"with the light that's directed underneath."},{"time":199999,"text":"With this approach, you could take a site"},{"time":201730,"text":"that looks like this today"},{"time":203941,"text":"and transform it into something"},{"time":205707,"text":"that looks like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207673,"text":"In 2011, we first released some of these images,"},{"time":211704,"text":"and what was funny was,"},{"time":213093,"text":"a lot of people said to us, \"Oh, it kind of looks"},{"time":215417,"text":"like the High Line underground.\""},{"time":217353,"text":"And so what our nickname ended up becoming,"},{"time":221673,"text":"and what ended up sticking,"},{"time":223473,"text":"was the Lowline, so the Lowline was born."},{"time":226319,"text":"What was also clear was that people really wanted"},{"time":227996,"text":"to know a lot more about how the technology"},{"time":229694,"text":"would look and feel,"},{"time":231260,"text":"and that there was really much more interest in this"},{"time":233393,"text":"than we had ever thought possible."},{"time":235488,"text":"So, like a crazy person, I decided to quit my job"},{"time":237727,"text":"and focus entirely on this project."},{"time":239921,"text":"Here is us with our team"},{"time":241743,"text":"putting together a technology demonstration"},{"time":244151,"text":"in a warehouse."},{"time":246170,"text":"Here's the underbelly of this solar canopy"},{"time":249270,"text":"which we built to show the technology."},{"time":251599,"text":"You can see the six solar collectors at the center there."},{"time":254479,"text":"And here's the full exhibit all put together"},{"time":257090,"text":"in this warehouse."},{"time":258541,"text":"You can see the solar canopy overhead,"},{"time":260318,"text":"the light streaming in,"},{"time":261734,"text":"and this entirely live green space below."},{"time":264358,"text":"So in the course of just a few weeks,"},{"time":265784,"text":"tens of thousands of people came to see our exhibit,"},{"time":269353,"text":"and since that time, we've grown"},{"time":270810,"text":"our numbers of supporters both locally"},{"time":273111,"text":"and among design enthusiasts all over the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":275823,"text":"Here's a rendering of the neighborhood"},{"time":277884,"text":"just immediately above the Line's site,"},{"time":280250,"text":"and a rendering of how it will look"},{"time":282384,"text":"after major redevelopment that is coming"},{"time":284668,"text":"over the course of the next 10 years."},{"time":286671,"text":"Notice how crowded the neighborhood still feels"},{"time":288786,"text":"and how there's really a lack of green space."},{"time":290710,"text":"So what we're proposing is really something that will"},{"time":293430,"text":"add one football field of green space"},{"time":297180,"text":"underneath this neighborhood, but more importantly"},{"time":300046,"text":"will introduce a really community-driven focus"},{"time":302760,"text":"in a rapidly gentrifying area."},{"time":304943,"text":"And right now, we're focusing very closely"},{"time":306687,"text":"on how we engage with the City of New York"},{"time":309106,"text":"on really transforming the overall ecosystem"},{"time":312549,"text":"in an integrated way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314630,"text":"Here's our rendering of how we would actually"},{"time":316239,"text":"invite people into the space itself."},{"time":318377,"text":"So here you see this iconic entrance"},{"time":320683,"text":"in which we would literally peel up the street"},{"time":322855,"text":"and reveal the historical layers of the city,"},{"time":325870,"text":"and invite people into this warm underground space."},{"time":328775,"text":"In the middle of winter, when it's\nabsolutely freezing outside,"},{"time":331034,"text":"the last place you'd want to go would be"},{"time":332124,"text":"an outdoor space or outdoor park."},{"time":334634,"text":"The Lowline would really be a four-season space"},{"time":336559,"text":"and a respite for the city."},{"time":339045,"text":"So I like to think that the Lowline actually brings"},{"time":341363,"text":"my own family's story full circle."},{"time":343984,"text":"If my grandparents and my parents were really"},{"time":345918,"text":"focused on building the city up and out,"},{"time":349205,"text":"I think my generation is focused on reclaiming"},{"time":351281,"text":"the spaces that we already have,"},{"time":353189,"text":"rediscovering our shared history,"},{"time":355146,"text":"and reimagining how we can make our communities"},{"time":357724,"text":"more interesting, more beautiful and more just."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360737,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362706,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}